headline: CPRT Q3 Deep Dive: Market Share Pressures Weigh Amid Mixed Insurance and Auction Trends
summary: Online vehicle auction company Copart (NASDAQ:CPRT) fell short of the markets revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales flat year on year at $1.16 billion. Its GAAP profit of $0.41 per share was 3.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
